{
  "key": 58407,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_WhatsThisAbout",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} examined the ancient\n",
        "cave painting.\r",
        "Mysterious designs cover a whole\n",
        "section of the wall.\r",
        "There are three strange things\n",
        "forming a triangle.\r",
        "In the middle of them, a shining\n",
        "sphere?\r",
        "What is this all about?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_AncientLegendOfSinnoh",
      "en_US": [
        "The cave painting’s meaning seems\n",
        "to be this...\r",
        "There existed beings...\r",
        "The three kept balance with either\n",
        "being, as if they formed a pyramid.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_IdLikeToKnowMore",
      "en_US": [
        "???: I would like to know more about\n",
        "that legend, if you will.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_WhoMightYouBe",
      "en_US": "Elder: Who might you be...?\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_MyNameIsCyrus",
      "en_US": [
        "My name is Cyrus.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_NotInterested",
      "en_US": [
        "Elder: I wouldn’t know.\n",
        "I do know the world is in balance.\r",
        "I’m quite satisfied with the world the\n",
        "way it is.\r",
        "I’m not interested in your question.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_ChallengeMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: ...Plead ignorance, will you?\n",
        "If you feel that way, challenge me.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_WellChallengeMe",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: Well? Am I wrong?\n",
        "If you feel that way, challenge me.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_ErrorOfYourWays",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: ...I know you, Trainer.\n",
        "show you the error of your ways.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_YouChoseCoward",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: ...You chose to be a coward.\n",
        "How sensible of you.\r",
        "Stand aside and watch as I change\n",
        "the world."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_YouChoseCoward2",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: ...You chose to be a coward.\n",
        "How sensible of you.\r",
        "Stand aside and watch as I change\n",
        "the world.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_Remarkable",
      "en_US": [
        "Cyrus: ...Remarkable.\r",
        "But, Elder, your attitude told me what\n",
        "I needed to know.\r",
        "If the beings of time and space are\n",
        "brought together, they can’t be\f",
        "stopped...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_WeValueMemories",
      "en_US": [
        "That cave painting isn’t protected\n",
        "What world could he dream of?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_YouShouldTakeThis",
      "en_US": [
        "You should take this.\r",
        "It belonged to my granddaughter,\n",
        "but she doesn’t use it anymore.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_SurfAcrossWater",
      "en_US": [
        "If a Pokémon learns Surf, it can\n",
        "carry you across water and the sea.\r",
        "You’ve been a great help.\n",
        "That’s my thanks for it.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_PlayerExaminedPainting",
      "en_US": [
        "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} examined the ancient\n",
        "cave painting.\r",
        "Mysterious designs cover a whole\n",
        "section of the wall.\r",
        "There are three strange things forming\n",
        "a triangle.\r",
        "In the middle of them, a shining\n",
        "sphere..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_PaintingDescribedThisWay",
      "en_US": [
        "Cynthia: This cave painting...\n",
        "It’s always been described this way.\r",
        "The light in the center represents\n",
        "either DIALGA or PALKIA appearing\f",
        "at the Spear Pillar.\r",
        "The three lights around it were thought\n",
        "to be UXIE, MESPRIT, and AZELF.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_MayIContinue",
      "en_US": "May I continue?"
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_OtherInterpretationContinueLonger",
      "en_US": [
        "Cynthia: But, then, I realized that\n",
        "there may be another way of\f",
        "interpreting this.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_ThanksForListening",
      "en_US": [
        "Cynthia: Thank you for listening to\n",
        "my theory.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_NotSureHowGiratinaFits",
      "en_US": [
        "I’m not quite sure how GIRATINA fits\n",
        "into this scheme of things, but...\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_MayISayLastBit",
      "en_US": [
        "I’m sorry this is so long.\n",
        "May I say one last bit?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_ThatsWhatIBelieve",
      "en_US": [
        "I think I let myself get carried away\n",
        "and talked for far too long.\r",
        "I’m sorry, and thank you.\n",
        "Let’s meet again.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "CelesticTownCave_Text_IGotCarriedAway",
      "en_US": [
        "I’m so sorry.\n",
        "I let myself get carried away...\r"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
